15/* RFC 4255 */

17#ifndef RDATA_GENERIC_SSHFP_44_C
18#define RDATA_GENERIC_SSHFP_44_C

20#define RRTYPE_SSHFP_ATTRIBUTES (0)

22static inline isc_result_t
23fromtext_sshfp(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
24 isc_token_t token;
25
26 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_sshfp);
27
28 UNUSED(type);
29 UNUSED(rdclass);
30 UNUSED(origin);
31 UNUSED(options);
32 UNUSED(callbacks);
33
34 /*
35 * Algorithm.
36 */
37 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
38 false));
39 if (token.value.as_ulong > 0xffU)
40 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
41 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
42
43 /*
44 * Digest type.
45 */
46 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
47 false));
48 if (token.value.as_ulong > 0xffU)
49 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
50 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
51
52 /*
53 * Digest.
54 */
55 return (isc_hex_tobuffer(lexer, target, -2));
56}
57
58static inline isc_result_t
59totext_sshfp(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
60 isc_region_t sr;
61 char buf[sizeof("64000 ")];
62 unsigned int n;
63
64 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_sshfp);
65 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
66
67 UNUSED(tctx);
68
69 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
70
71 /*
72 * Algorithm.
73 */
74 n = uint8_fromregion(&sr);
75 isc_region_consume(&sr, 1);
76 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u ", n);
77 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
78
79 /*
80 * Digest type.
81 */
82 n = uint8_fromregion(&sr);
83 isc_region_consume(&sr, 1);
84 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u", n);
85 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
86
87 /*
88 * Digest.
89 */
90 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_MULTILINE) != 0)
91 RETERR(str_totext(" (", target));
92 RETERR(str_totext(tctx->linebreak, target));
93 if (tctx->width == 0) /* No splitting */
94 RETERR(isc_hex_totext(&sr, 0, "", target));
95 else
96 RETERR(isc_hex_totext(&sr, tctx->width - 2,
97 tctx->linebreak, target));
98 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_MULTILINE) != 0)
99 RETERR(str_totext(" )", target));
100 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
101}

103static inline isc_result_t
104fromwire_sshfp(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
105 isc_region_t sr;
106
107 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_sshfp);
108
109 UNUSED(type);
110 UNUSED(rdclass);
111 UNUSED(dctx);
112 UNUSED(options);
113
114 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &sr);
115 if (sr.length < 4)
116 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
117
118 isc_buffer_forward(source, sr.length);
119 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, sr.length));
120}
121
122static inline isc_result_t
123towire_sshfp(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
124 isc_region_t sr;
125
126 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_sshfp);
127 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
128
129 UNUSED(cctx);
130
131 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
132 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, sr.length));
133}

135static inline int
136compare_sshfp(ARGS_COMPARE) {
137 isc_region_t r1;
138 isc_region_t r2;
139
140 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
141 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
142 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_sshfp);
143 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
144 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
145
146 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &r1);
147 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &r2);
148 return (isc_region_compare(&r1, &r2));
149}
150
151static inline isc_result_t
152fromstruct_sshfp(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
153 dns_rdata_sshfp_t *sshfp = source;
154
155 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_sshfp);
156 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
157 REQUIRE(sshfp->common.rdtype == type);
158 REQUIRE(sshfp->common.rdclass == rdclass);
159
160 UNUSED(type);
161 UNUSED(rdclass);
162
163 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(sshfp->algorithm, target));
164 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(sshfp->digest_type, target));
165
166 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sshfp->digest, sshfp->length));
167}
168
169static inline isc_result_t
170tostruct_sshfp(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
171 dns_rdata_sshfp_t *sshfp = target;
172 isc_region_t region;
173
174 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_sshfp);
175 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
176 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
177
178 sshfp->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
179 sshfp->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
180 ISC_LINK_INIT(&sshfp->common, link);
181
182 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
183
184 sshfp->algorithm = uint8_fromregion(&region);
185 isc_region_consume(&region, 1);
186 sshfp->digest_type = uint8_fromregion(&region);
187 isc_region_consume(&region, 1);
188 sshfp->length = region.length;
189
190 sshfp->digest = mem_maybedup(mctx, region.base, region.length);
191 if (sshfp->digest == NULL)
192 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
193
194 sshfp->mctx = mctx;
195 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
196}
197
198static inline void
199freestruct_sshfp(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
200 dns_rdata_sshfp_t *sshfp = source;
201
202 REQUIRE(sshfp != NULL);
203 REQUIRE(sshfp->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_sshfp);
204
205 if (sshfp->mctx == NULL)
206 return;
207
208 if (sshfp->digest != NULL)
209 isc_mem_free(sshfp->mctx, sshfp->digest);
210 sshfp->mctx = NULL;
211}

213static inline isc_result_t
214additionaldata_sshfp(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
215 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_sshfp);
216
217 UNUSED(rdata);
218 UNUSED(add);
219 UNUSED(arg);
220
221 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
222}

224static inline isc_result_t
225digest_sshfp(ARGS_DIGEST) {
226 isc_region_t r;
227
228 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_sshfp);
229
230 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
231
232 return ((digest)(arg, &r));
233}

260static inline int
261casecompare_sshfp(ARGS_COMPARE) {
262 return (compare_sshfp(rdata1, rdata2));
